est serfis/terminations to the strokes. Rho is open; Sigma is four-bar, with very shallow middle strokes; Mu has all four strokes oblique, with the middle strokes only half-height.",[291,294],{"type":43,"l":292,"from":45,"to":51,"h":293,"unit":47},"Lines 1-2","25-28",{"type":49,"l":50,"from":45,"to":51,"h":239,"unit":47},{"_":296,"notBefore":55,"notAfter":143,"precision":18},"1st — 2nd century CE",[298,299],{"_":59,"type":60,"ref":61},{"_":63,"type":64,"ref":65},[301],[68,69],[],{"_":76,"role":77,"ref":78},{"_":155,"mainLang":152,"languages":305},[155],"645531",{"n":88,"url":308,"height":90,"width":91,"desc":309,"surfaceType":93},"ISic003208_tiled.tif","I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2016-05-13.",[],[262,97,98],[265,101,102],[314,315,316,280,20,24,107,108,109,110,108,111,212,152],"isic003208","fragment of an honorary inscription?",{"_":124},"\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.\u003C/span>ΙΑ · Ι · ΡΗ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>ψηφί]σμα πα̣[ρὰ? \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"author":3,"date":4,"citedRange":272,"ptr":319,"ref":320,"title":2,"citation":5,"uri":6},{"target":117},{"_":119,"target":119},{"file":322,"uri":322,"title":323,"status":324,"editionAuthor":13,"type":325,"objectType":327,"material":329,"condition":330,"layoutDesc":331,"handNote":337,"date":347,"places":350,"geo":354,"provenance":59,"provenanceGeo":356,"country":73,"regio